{"tid":2249351,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「開明建制派」陳謳明掌聖公會","createTime":"2020-10-19T09:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T10:05:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9f71fcbf177c13673e36a5f14eefeb09d79073c9","tid":2249351,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/XUEVATI32ZBJ3IJM7BDH4ANL2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FXUEVATI32ZBJ3IJM7BDH4ANL2A%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Zltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=30958d6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FXUEVATI32ZBJ3IJM7BDH4ANL2A%2F&h=154963d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/XUEVATI32ZBJ3IJM7BDH4ANL2A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「開明建制派」陳謳明掌聖公會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8bnT5I7CyM7fOuEUMBi7GBtdavk=/1481x1057/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DBGI3L7TOJDIZLDAHHNQVKDX64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8bnT5I7CyM7fOuEUMBi7GBtdavk%3D%2F1481x1057%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDBGI3L7TOJDIZLDAHHNQVKDX64.jpg&h=bfaa9398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳謳明（左圖）當選聖公會下任大主教，接替年底退休的鄺保羅（右圖）。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。。。。。聖公會昨宣佈，下午召開第八屆總議會大主教選舉團特別會議後，由陳謳明主教獲得選舉團三院各逾半數贊成票，當選為香港聖公會下任大主教。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾籲林鄭為送中例道歉<br />\n<br />\n香港聖公會《教省規例》規定，當選的大主教候選人，須在選舉團內的主教院、聖品院與平信徒院（選舉團三院）分別得票最多，且各獲半數贊成票。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n現年58歲的聖公會西九龍教區主教陳謳明被形容為「開明建制派」，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳謳明亦至少兩次在聖公會就社會事件發表的牧函中署名，包括就去年6月反修例運動，指事件是來自政府忽略市民聲音及恐懼，表示盼望特首林鄭月娥就事件致歉，並對年輕人抱持赤子之心、為理想站出來感到欣喜，但強調教會對暴力堅持「說不」；及後就7.1衝擊立法會事件，表示尊重以和平理性方式表達不滿，但強調不接受「暴力行為」，同時呼籲港府以行動回應港人訴求。"},{"pid":"73d61ca922cf87775fefca6e83e2d1f764feb159","tid":2249351,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:37:56.000Z","msg":"管浩鳴呢，幫牙佳搞咁多大龍鳳都得個桔？"},{"pid":"f9d3b787e5ea10cff107453d13b41df4d724d05b","tid":2249351,"uid":282347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:39:24.000Z","msg":"一睇相就知係另一個奶共撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又扮中立想食兩家茶禮"},{"pid":"4c3d80c6a28b74c85e9d3c179f3f3560645a4054","tid":2249351,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73d61ca922cf87775fefca6e83e2d1f764feb159","tid":2249351,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:37:56.000Z","msg":"管浩鳴呢，幫牙佳搞咁多大龍鳳都得個桔？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:40:14.000Z","msg":"人仲要幫佳仔出火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d3d4eb2e43e94a6354eb02e0065d4dd1ee54b0","tid":2249351,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9d3b787e5ea10cff107453d13b41df4d724d05b","tid":2249351,"uid":282347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:39:24.000Z","msg":"一睇相就知係另一個奶共撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又扮中立想食兩家茶禮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:41:22.000Z","msg":"奶共方面開明呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512d1d998f679c4e8b33c5e36a92d9a7debb9218","tid":2249351,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"呢D仆街神職人員一定落硬地獄"},{"pid":"008d9f16fa64b358365f365613c0cc366dbaaee7","tid":2249351,"uid":210755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:43:33.000Z","msg":"親共點會有開明, 陰啲陰啲咁陰乾你呀，企喺親共嗰邊 一係同化成魔,一係搞到一獲泡"},{"pid":"b05acf943af661f89ce5e66bcdd4e6293d64f4fd","tid":2249351,"uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:48:48.000Z","msg":"又要提老毛<br />\n當年老毛如果嫌知識份子、<br />\n細生意老闆(城市小知產階級)<br />\n大老闆(民族資產階級)等唔夠左、唔配同佢同一陣線<br />\n今日大陸仲係中華民國<br />\n<br />\n連登仔想贏，睇下近代史啦唔該<br />\n要贏，唔單止泛民係統戰對象<br />\n連呢位陳主教、甚至自由黨都係<br />\n<br />\n唔識團結大多數，唔好妄想贏"},{"pid":"2cc428180afac509753424e1de812dcf445c1025","tid":2249351,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:51:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb860c2f6ec469640162ac5b9f90af8e9cbb29a2","tid":2249351,"uid":239270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:51:23.000Z","msg":"習總都係進步獨裁者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca03e7b5c029c5cf778f388a35b9cc3400c41f07","tid":2249351,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:53:54.000Z","msg":"即係曾鈺成之流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d6ea49b16f7c941bf1bab3985e52e75f735e58","tid":2249351,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:54:18.000Z","msg":"所謂開明建制派=禁慾性派對"},{"pid":"a97aadc65a274103c7199ed61774ffe90ff42581","tid":2249351,"uid":285165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:05:18.000Z","msg":"開明建制派<br />\n我以為白頭佬佢地渣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}